Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:04.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The rhythm of the wind clears reasoning,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.77,0:00:06.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Always unveiling alibi tricks.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:08.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Danger is still in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.23,0:00:10.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll have to be sharp to capture the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.28,0:00:12.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.99,0:00:14.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.99,0:00:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His name is Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.33,0:01:47.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We all became worried after waiting so long for Hattori and Kazuha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.00,0:01:49.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We went to search for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.04,0:01:58.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After discovering they went to visit a detective named Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, we went to his house for clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I bet you're hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.27,0:02:07.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you'll have to wait just a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.27,0:02:08.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mama's busy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.10,0:02:11.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I finish my lecture,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:13.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll feed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:16.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:18.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Teach this boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.45,0:02:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,About how desperate his situation really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.53,0:02:25.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He'll learn to play by my rules from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.42,0:02:36.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori Heiji's Desperate Situation, Part Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.84,0:02:42.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, those Osaka kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:45.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.10,0:02:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Dad, let's visit the rest of the Ito's after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.73,0:02:53.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Maybe we just missed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:03:00.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Someone as famous as myself shouldn't be seen in such a cheap restaurant...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.74,0:03:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no helping it, we originally planned to have those two with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:09.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, I like the classic feel of this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:11.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:16.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You won't find one of these horoscope machines anywhere else these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:20.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, call them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.84,0:03:23.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They may be waiting at my office now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.97,0:03:28.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've been calling often, but no one has...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.10,0:03:30.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.89,0:03:31.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.40,0:03:36.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:39.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat! Where are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.07,0:03:40.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:47.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I met up with a guy named Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} to talk about some cases and just forgot to call you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And Kazuha{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}'s there with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.00,0:03:53.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, don't worry about her. She's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.54,0:03:55.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway Uncle,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.13,0:03:58.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have a code I want you to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.80,0:03:59.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A code?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:02.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} created.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.59,0:04:05.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I promised him I wouldn't leave until I cracked it,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.05,0:04:07.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,but it's taking awhile.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.22,0:04:11.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need you to solve it before he comes back.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.98,0:04:14.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.77,0:04:23.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, some of his persistent friends want him to be the last player in a game of Mahjong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.03,0:04:30.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Anyway, I'll mail you the code now. I need the answer by sundown.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.12,0:04:34.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need you to get the seven digit answer for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.25,0:04:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seven digit answer?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.04,0:04:41.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I won't be able to visit you all unless you solve it. Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.96,0:04:43.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.26,0:04:44.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.26,0:04:53.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How clever of you to make Mouri Kogoro handle it
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.85,0:04:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.23,0:04:59.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's mail the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.61,0:05:05.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We can't, this guy got his blood over the bottom half.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:06.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What'd you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.16,0:05:08.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't you make a copy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:12.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I spent most of my time torturing Kusukawa after we broke in to get it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.95,0:05:15.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I remember it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,All forty-nine numbers and alphabet letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.38,0:05:23.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.55,0:05:27.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright then, why don't you recite all of it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.59,0:05:32.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You better not mess upon the top part...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.72,0:05:37.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or you'll find yourself covered in your girlfriend's blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.19,0:05:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the hell's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.19,0:05:44.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.57,0:05:50.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Many numbers with the alphabet letters "Q A K J."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.20,0:05:52.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.99,0:05:56.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This just makes no sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Hattori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wouldn't go against his word and leave, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.54,0:06:01.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.75,0:06:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you get something, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.13,0:06:05.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.55,0:06:07.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:13.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, the only letters in it, "A J Q K," are like playing cards, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.68,0:06:15.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So I changed them to numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.22,0:06:16.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:23.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now we have sixty-four numbers, but there's one lonely number.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:28.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! The nine in the middle. It only occurs once.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.82,0:06:34.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you remove the nine, we get sixty-three; which is divisible by nine, giving us seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:44.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think that each of the seven groups represents a single digit, that is, if it's for seven digits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:47.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's a lot harder than math, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:48.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seems so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.97,0:06:53.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Jeez, it's just a bunch of non-sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.22,0:06:56.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here is your diced steak, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here's your kids meal, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:10.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey Uncle, by any chance was the creator of the code Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:12.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:16.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, that's why nine is in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.37,0:07:19.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here you are, enjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:21.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.00,0:07:22.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like I've almost got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.71,0:07:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.59,0:07:32.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's strange. The first four are letters, but the rest are...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.76,0:07:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, I've seen this somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:46.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh my, look at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.73,0:07:51.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have to go, as the bank's closing soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:56.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you have to blame someone, blame the detective who failed to solve it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:08:00.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, he may get it if he can think it over tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.29,0:08:05.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You just need to get the pin number before the package gets to the detective agency, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.33,0:08:07.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't be delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.09,0:08:11.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You wouldn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.84,0:08:14.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, tomorrow morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.97,0:08:19.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In front of the detective agency, we'll ambush the mailman.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.81,0:08:26.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll kill him, steal Kusukawa's tape, and that will be that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.52,0:08:31.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tape will be hidden forever so long as I pay the rental fee.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.94,0:08:35.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That code is no longer important, because unlike you, I have many years left.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.28,0:08:40.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, if you have anything left to say, here's your chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.62,0:08:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As an attorney, it's my job to have sympathetic ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:48.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shit. Damn you, Kudo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.25,0:08:50.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell are you doing!?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.09,0:08:54.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, it's time to say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.43,0:08:56.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you have nothing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:59.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-N-No, I do have some final words.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.01,0:09:03.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was just thinking of the most important thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.52,0:09:08.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll have to direct my final words to the girl behind me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.69,0:09:16.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh? What's there to say? Your girlfriend won't last much longer than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:20.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's something I've wanted to tell her forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:26.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Will you put the gun down until I'm finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:30.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, you are high schoolers after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.71,0:09:32.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pardon my inconsideration.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.01,0:09:35.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:39.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.84,0:09:41.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, give me a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:45.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to make sure it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.23,0:09:54.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want it to be perfect, so she'll always remember it in heaven.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:09:59.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This guy's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Damn
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that's too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:07.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't a bad plan to get the gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.08,0:10:09.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that was a "plan"?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.13,0:10:10.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:17.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like we were lucky enough to have you tell us this guy wasn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:26.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now, tell us the answer. You don't want these kids to die, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.02,0:10:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.31,0:10:34.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Telling them the truth would only delay our deaths.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.90,0:10:37.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's not give them the satisfaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.24,0:10:40.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shut up, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:41.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.33,0:10:45.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll give you five seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.62,0:10:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believe me when I say, I won't hesitate to shoot the boy with so little time left
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.00,0:10:53.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Trust me, Kazuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:01.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I meant it when I said my last words were for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.85,0:11:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Again and again, I almost said it...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:09.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,4...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:13.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time I felt you tremble against my back...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.88,0:11:35.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.13,0:11:38.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from Mouri Kogoro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.71,0:11:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think he solved that code?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:43.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look like an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:49.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Looks like he just sent the mail back, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.64,0:11:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it looks like the letters and numbers were re-arranged.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.44,0:11:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey lady, let me see it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:01.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,N-No, I mean, may I please see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:04.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Here, this is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it look almost identical to the original code?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.41,0:12:13.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're alike...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.58,0:12:15.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Except this one's the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.17,0:12:21.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I mean is: all seven digits are in this code.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.13,0:12:24.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You aren't bluffing, are you!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.30,0:12:25.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.26,0:12:28.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not saying it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.35,0:12:32.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now boy, do you understand your predictament?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:34.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do, but do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mouri Kogoro knows the answer to the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:46.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He also knows Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} created it and that we're with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.16,0:12:52.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since all three of us went missing at once, he will wonder about the meaning of the seven numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.08,0:13:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It won't take him long to trace the seven digits back to the rental locker rented by Kusuakawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} at Tohto bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:08.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you involve Mouri Kogoro knowing this would happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't good, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:12.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Should we kill them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.68,0:13:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't get anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.85,0:13:16.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You only have two choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:22.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kill us and run, allowing Mouri Kogoro to find the tape and expose your tax schemes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or, you could have me get the tape, and release us three in exchange for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.03,0:13:36.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It could be Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, but his face is injured and can't be seen in public.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.29,0:13:43.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry though, I'm offering the same deal as Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} did:
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.30,0:13:51.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You must cease all illegal operations, including your tax fraud scheme, and start on a clean slate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Do you think we're stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.56,0:13:57.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're planning to run to the police with the tape, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you don't believe me, have someone come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:04.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I do anything suspicious, you can kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.28,0:14:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There isn't much time left. I think that bank's closing pretty soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:16.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:19.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But boy, let me warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.00,0:14:25.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the code's wrong, you'll be dead in a minute. Understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.97,0:14:36.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll go with the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Girl, you'll stay here with this man and be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:42.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.40,0:14:44.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Kazuha?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.94,0:14:47.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we... If we survive this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we survive this, will you tell me what you were going to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.12,0:14:58.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Until you're tired of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.09,0:15:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Heiji...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.10,0:15:28.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's gasoline. When she calls and says she has the tape, we'll set the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.53,0:15:37.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That boy will be surprised to find his friends not outside waiting, but still up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.21,0:15:44.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright boy, hurry, put in the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.67,0:15:49.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Rut in the secret pin number.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:53.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, aren't you interested in the decoding system?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:56.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who cares, save that for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.76,0:16:05.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By knowing that Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gambles, you should instantly recognize "A J Q K" from playing cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.23,0:16:10.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When you convert them over, you get sixty-four numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.61,0:16:14.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The key is the nine in the middle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:19.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One through six occur often, but nine only occurs once.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:27.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, I removed the nine. This leaves us with sixty-three numbers, giving us seven groups of nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.71,0:16:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought that maybe each group was of nine numbers, giving us one digit per column for the seven digit pin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.34,0:16:37.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Also, the numbers go only from one to six.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.14,0:16:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, one through six refers to one thing in gambling.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.35,0:16:44.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:51.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The code is telling you to map each row into a three-by-three box.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.53,0:16:58.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, how does that make up seven digits?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.87,0:17:02.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Imagine each number on a die and order them as it specifies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.46,0:17:07.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The red spots should stand out now, making it simply:
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.46,0:17:11.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,3, 1, 5, 6, 2, 0, 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:18.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And... 3, 1, 5, 6, 2, 0, 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.26,0:17:26.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is probably because it can be read as "throw the dice."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Look, it opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.48,0:17:32.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.57,0:17:34.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The tape you're after?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.82,0:17:38.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm pretty sure it is. Hurry, hand it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.49,0:17:41.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, I have one more thing to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.37,0:17:46.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That secret code I sent to Mouri Kogoro...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.54,0:17:51.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The last part's numbers were changed to letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.00,0:17:54.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.34,0:17:58.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One capital letter and two lower case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:00.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"L I B."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.72,0:18:06.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the three letter abbreviation for Libra.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:08.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Libra?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What? You don't get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.77,0:18:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've got it on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.07,0:18:17.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The scales of order: your attorney's badge!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.45,0:18:22.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, that means Mouri Kogoro is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:27.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,From what I saw in his mail, he should be finished by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.83,0:18:28.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mail?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.29,0:18:31.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Lure out"
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He meant for me to decrease your numbers by luring one of you out
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:38.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This just can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:40.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.80,0:18:44.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't have a hand worth betting on.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:48.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.52,0:18:50.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come out if you're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.85,0:18:53.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hurry, don't slack off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:56.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She's back early...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:59.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sensei, did you forget to...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.45,0:19:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.67,0:19:17.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.80,0:19:20.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:29.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I still have no idea what's going on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:33.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But since he knew I'd call the police, this is probably what he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.03,0:19:41.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The police came soon after and released Kazuha and Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.32,0:19:46.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With the arrest of the scandalous lawyer and her accomplices,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.58,0:19:52.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,all of the tax evasion and kidnapping cases were closed immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.72,0:21:29.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tricked those two by using that woman's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.01,0:21:33.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finished them with a tranquilizer and soccer ball?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's great, Kudo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.89,0:21:37.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.98,0:21:41.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had to sneak out of the restroom at this restaurant
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.57,0:21:47.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But hold on, Kudo, this wouldn't have gotten so complicated if you hadn't of left at that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.24,0:21:52.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could I have known a woman like that would take you all hostage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.41,0:21:56.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.21,0:21:59.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your kid's meal is getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.00,0:22:01.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.38,0:22:05.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A kid's meal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.88,0:22:09.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ran's always treating me like a kid, ordering that stuff for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.10,0:22:13.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But this time it served as a hint
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.64,0:22:17.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, the Japanese flag does look like the red on a die.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.56,0:22:22.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By the way, why did Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} try to just get her to stop?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.90,0:22:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The press would have been all over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:30.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, it seems that she saved Kusukawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s mother in the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.49,0:22:37.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,She helped her when she was scammed badly, and ever since, she has worshiped her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.54,0:22:43.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems he just wanted to protect his mother's feelings, but I knew I had to expose her no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.71,0:22:47.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Believe me though, I am grateful to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.05,0:22:49.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was really close in many ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.30,0:22:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,By "really close,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.39,0:22:55.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,do you mean when you were talking about your final words?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:22:57.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kazuha...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.68,0:22:58.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.27,0:23:02.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The thing you almost said every time I trembled.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.61,0:23:05.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You don't wanna know...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.03,0:23:08.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You said you'd tell me 'til I got tired of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.15,0:23:10.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.82,0:23:14.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, what I was gonna say was...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.95,0:23:15.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:17.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:23.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was... Every time you trembled...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.42,0:23:25.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Every time...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.09,0:23:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your ponytail kept brushing up against my neck over and over, it got so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.06,0:23:39.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's what it was, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.39,0:23:42.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,SORRY THEN!
